  <title translate="true">MT-POP-Motion Laws</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword translate="true">Cam-Law</keyword>
    <keyword translate="true">Motion-Law</keyword>
    <keyword translate="true">Segment Type</keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:none;"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="1" style="width:450px;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Motion-Law</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">: the name of the function</text><text styleclass="BodyText Bold" style="font-size:10pt;" translate="true">*</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> that you apply to each segment. The name of the </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Motion-Law</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> is usually derived from the:</text></para>
          <list id="0" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Shape of the Acceleration graph - e.g. Modified Trapezoid</text></li>
          </list>
          <list id="1" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Mathematical definition - e.g. Triple Harmonic, Cubic</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Motion function - e.g. Constant-Velocity, Dwell</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">The math is based on Polynomial or Harmonic functions.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Each </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Motion-Law</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> has advantages and disadvantages. Thus, you should select a</text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true"> Motion-Law</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> for the application. Frequently, there is not a perfect law for the application.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="BodyText Bold" style="font-size:10pt;" translate="true">*</text><text styleclass="Body Table" style="font-size:10pt;" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">You do </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">not</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> need to know any Mathematics.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Other terms for </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Motion-Law</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> are: </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Cam-Law</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> or </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Segment Type</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="SeeAlso-small"><text styleclass="SeeAlso-small" translate="true">See </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Motion-Cam-Laws" styleclass="SeeAlso-small" translate="true">Motion-Laws</link><text styleclass="SeeAlso-small" translate="true"> for more details.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:none;"></para>
